	                    </div>
	                    <div class="dsq-comment-body" id="dsq-comment-body-1505391322">
	                        <div class="dsq-comment-header">
	                            <span class="dsq-comment-date">2014-07-26</span>
	                            <span class="dsq-commenter-name">weaverryan</span>
