	                                <p>Figured out the problem. You need the following under the 'secured_area:' under your 'firewalls:' in security.yml</p><p>            form_login:<br>      check_path: login_check<br>      login_path: login</p><p>instead of</p><p>            form_login:<br>     check_path: /login/check<br>     login_path: /login</p><p>This forum doesn't allow tab characters, apparently, so the above may look a little funny compared to what it should look like in your actual file...</p>
